# [#22] End-to-End Integration Tests for Critical Workflows

> **GitHub**: https://github.com/kanya01/COLABS/issues/22
> **Opened**: 2026-01-14
> **Labels**: `epic:services-workflow` `testing` `integration` `quality`
> **Assignee**: —
> **Parent**: [[Issues/Open/[#55] Implement testing strategy for front end typescript components]]
> **Ref**: Services Workflow Implementation Issues #16

## Description

Create integration tests for complete workflows from service creation to payout.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Booking flow** — tier selection → PaymentIntent → mock Stripe confirm → order created → earning created
- [ ] **Seller payout flow** — Connect account → complete orders → hold period → request payout → verify payout & earnings
- [ ] **Order lifecycle test** — create → status transitions → revisions → deliverables → complete
- [ ] **Webhook integration tests** — payment, Connect, and Transfer webhooks
- [ ] Mock external Stripe API calls
- [ ] Use realistic test data
- [ ] Verify database state at each step

